Package org.crsh.cmdline.annotations

Annotation Types Summary
Argument Annotates a field or parameter to become an command line argument.
Command Annotate something that can be a command or be involved in a command.
Man The most verbose description intended for the manual.
Option Annotates a field or parameter to become an command line option.
Required Defines wether an argument or option is required or not.
Usage Describes shortly in one line an usage.
